{"tid":1996161,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"為西環「釋法」補鑊 鄭若驊亂拋憲法　變搞社會主義法治","createTime":"2020-04-30T19:15:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-30T19:34:53.000Z","uid":279819,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6e08cae8842257159f4efc675d4b03b2aa1b2e2c","tid":1996161,"uid":279819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T19:15:27.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】中聯辦自稱有「監督權」干預港事務，稱不受《基本法》第22條規管，遭轟如「太上皇」。律政司長鄭若驊試圖拋出憲法第五條作最新說辭，作為規管中聯辦需遵守香港法律的法理基礎，卻引來另一憲制問題，因第五條表明要「建設社會主義法治國家」，令人質疑中聯辦是否也要按憲法要求，在港「建設社會主義法治國家」。法律界人士批評，鄭為幫中聯辦曲解《基本法》，「噏得就噏」引用憲法，引發更多憲制問題與爭議。記者：陳珏明<br />\n,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,"},{"pid":"c2cf32d350ea8afdd44d73e49d4facfd3930617e","tid":1996161,"uid":279819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T19:20:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200501/TFOGBR7OL5SYYGOI6SVQPN4EBU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200501%2FTFOGBR7OL5SYYGOI6SVQPN4EBU%2F&d=IJrjZyikD9iZithZGIL3rAPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=fee5c3a3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200501%2FTFOGBR7OL5SYYGOI6SVQPN4EBU%2F&h=2d17edad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200501/TFOGBR7OL5SYYGOI6SVQPN4EBU/</a>"},{"pid":"2961ab1c6bffceb505e68c540823e42ed78b4e24","tid":1996161,"uid":279819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T19:24:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rQ9LvXG.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrQ9LvXG.gif&h=a726f674&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"790e83c93f16b3cb6029256d6f2ff8a21008a419","tid":1996161,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T19:34:53.000Z","msg":"支那憲法攞黎擺"}]}